The english manual in plain text format is in Manual.txt.
It is also available in html: start at Manual-HTML/Manual.html.
The sgml source is in Manual.sgml.

A german translation is also available:
in plain text: Manual-ger.txt
In html: start at Manual-ger-HTML/Manual.html.
sgml source: Manual-ger.sgml.

Also, we have a web page at http://www.cam.org/~nico/brltty.
